# ERROR TIPS
### Errors when using burner entities without fuel
- Ensure that the burner entities have sufficient fuel before using them.
### Errors when using entities without ingredients
- Ensure that the entities have the necessary ingredients before using them.
### Errors when using steam engine without connection
- Ensure that the steam engine is connected to a power source before using it.
### Errors when using pipe groups without fluid
- Ensure that the pipe groups have sufficient fluid before using them.
### Errors when using electricity groups without connection to electric network
- Ensure that the electricity groups are connected to an electric network before using them.
### Errors when using transport belt system without items
- Ensure that the transport belt system has items to transport before using it.
